Output examples/gifs/builtin-tools-review.gif

Set Shell cmd
Set Height 820
Set Width 1500
Set Framerate 18
Set FontSize 26

Hide
  Type `set PATH=%CD%\examples\demo-bin;%PATH% && cls`
  Enter
  Sleep 300ms
Show

Sleep 500ms
Type@25ms `mods --review mutable --workspace . "Read README.md and write docs/cli-notes.md with a short usage guide"`
Sleep 400ms
Enter
Sleep 2500ms
Type@80ms `y`
Sleep 200ms
Enter
Sleep 4s
